caption:
On this fine day in January, let’s remember that not only is hope around the corner but so is summer. In celebration, here’s a Level-10 smoke show. I’m about to pull that fire alarm behind him and drag him back to the security line so I can play TSA agent and give him a full pat down. #ShoesOff #BeltOff #EverythingOff 
#NowTakeMeToTerminalD #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

Wooooof. Who doesn’t adore a man reading while ALSO toting his best friend around the city? My only worry is that with a bond that strong, I might have some stiff competition for the other spot in his bed. At least I can guarantee a lot less snoring #ButNoLessDrooling #NewMeaningToDoggyStyle  #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

Spotted: Pedro Pascal looking lost in a book like Joel in the tunnels of Kansas City. That ripped white t-shirt is doing things to me that even a health kit can't fix. I’m over here imagining him protecting me from the Infected, and it has my heart racing faster than if a Clicker was after me. 10/10 sure, yea, I’d let him infect me with his mushroom any day. #WhoreForHisCordyceps #hotdudesreading #thelastofus

Looks like this Ken’s traded in Malibu for the sandy shores of Waikiki.  With that polished, shiny physique, he’s striking a pose even Yoga Retreat Barbie would envy. No idea what he’s reading, but with every page he flips, he’s turning up the temps in my midsection. Perfect time to invite him inside for a snack. After all, I like my men like I like my peanut butter – smooth and creamy. #Why(Not)KiKi #InMyRoom #SpreadEm #hotdudesreading

Lost in the sands of Arrakis but spotted on the streets of Hollywood, this So-Cal cutie can charm the meanest of sandworms. With a face sculpted by Shai-Hulud himself and a gaze as intense as a Bene Gesserit’s stare, he’s the Muad’Dib to my Fremen heart. Who needs melange when you’ve got a man who can help you navigate the desert of your dried-up, sandy, crusty love life? #HowYouDune  #FremenyWithBenefits #hotdudesreading #dune
Writing this caption in Spanish so this hot plate of paella knows I’m good with the local tongue: ¿Come se dice, “yo qiero ‘tappa dat ass’”? #HowYouSay #Cucumber #hotdudesreading

Spotted this baseball babetown diving into ‘Attached,' and now I’m stuck daydreaming about our perfectly attached future. We can start by discussing our attachment styles over coffee, then we can analyze our relationship baggage over dinner, then we can move to my place and end with the realization that I'm an anxious one in serious need of secure bonding. #AndYes #HandcuffsInBedDoCount #hotdudesreading

When the seating options ran dry, this perched prince sought higher ground. We love a man who knows how to make the most of a crowded situation. Also glad he knows how to handle a ledge. I take up a lot of space in bed. #ImJustThatSHELFish #hotdudesreading

Don’t know what thoughts this chiseled charmer is brewing up as he reads 'Alchemy: The Surprising Power of Ideas That Don't Make Sense,’ but I’ve got some strong ideas of my own, and they’re making me dizzier than a bad chemistry experiment. I mean, I HAVE always had a special talent for blowing things up, especially when it comes to men. #SomeCallMeTheGrenade
#hotdudesreading
Normally I’m used to hunting hot dudes reading on the 4/5/6 line, but thanks to @maisonvalentino I spent the weekend spotting them all over Milan. #AndInMyHotel

Y'all - spotted this southern stud in Kansas City and I’m not okay. He’s so hot, even his book is bending over for him. Hold on to your hat, cowboy, because I’m about to saddle up and knock those boots six ways to Sunday. #ThenMonday #ThenTuesday #ThenMyFavorite #Humpday #hotdudesreading

Spotted: another beefy bookworm reading the @maisonvalentino edition of “A Little Life.” Maybe they’re both traveling to Milan for the Fashion show today. Looks like ill be bringing a +2. #HowDoYouSayMénageàtroisInItalian?

Watch the #ValentinoNarratives Fashion Show today on the @maisonvalentino Instagram live from Milan.
